54
00:04:43,083 --> 00:04:44,458
<i>Silene Oliveira.</i>

55
00:04:45,875 --> 00:04:48,166
<i>Itulah namaku saat cerita ini dimulai.</i>

56
00:04:51,416 --> 00:04:54,125
<i>Saat aku yakin kita bisa lari</i>
<i>dari rasa sakit,</i>

57
