<i>seperti polisi.</i>

58
00:04:59,291 --> 00:05:00,416
<i>Lari,</i>

59
00:05:01,291 --> 00:05:02,458
<i>menutup mata,</i>

60
00:05:03,291 --> 00:05:04,291
<i>dan bertahan.</i>

61
00:05:13,875 --> 00:05:16,041
<i>Tapi, di suatu titik,</i>
<i>kita selalu berhenti.</i>

62
00:05:18,208 --> 00:05:20,208
<i>Lalu semua rasa sakit itu melanda kita.</i>

63
00:05:24,083 --> 00:05:27,125
<i>Kita merasa tak berdaya</i>
<i>untuk menghindar lagi.</i>

64
00:05:35,916 --> 00:05:37,541
<i>Sepuluh hari aku bersembunyi.</i>

65
00:05:38,458 --> 00:05:42,416
<i>Memutar, berulang kali, gambar-gambar</i>
<i>dari kehidupanku bersama René.</i>

66
00:05:45,583 --> 00:05:48,625
<i>Memikirkan dia yang tak suka bank.</i>

67
00:05:49,791 --> 00:05:51,791
<i>Saat kami memutuskan untuk merampok.</i>

68
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:54,625
<i>Begitu saja,</i>

69
00:05:55,208 --> 00:05:57,750
<i>rasa sakitku memburuk.</i>

70
00:06:04,333 --> 00:06:06,125
<i>Begitu pula rasa bersalahku.</i>

71
00:06:06,833 --> 00:06:08,625
<i>Karena meninggalkan dia di sana.</i>

72
00:06:08,708 --> 00:06:11,208
<i>Berbaring di tanah basah, di bawah hujan,</i>

73
00:06:12,541 --> 00:06:14,708
<i>seolah René masih bisa merasakannya.</i>

74
00:06:17,666 --> 00:06:21,000
<i>Lalu kupikir aku harus berlari lebih cepat</i>
<i>dari sebelumnya.</i>

75
00:06:22,541 --> 00:06:24,958
<i>Agar duka itu tak mengikutiku.</i>

76
00:06:27,625 --> 00:06:28,750
<i>Aku tak berhenti.</i>

77
00:06:29,416 --> 00:06:31,625
<i>Sekalipun aku tiba di jalan buntu itu,</i>

78
00:06:31,708 --> 00:06:34,583
<i>saat pasukan komando</i>
<i>bertekad membunuh kami.</i>

79
00:06:35,166 --> 00:06:36,666
<i>Di titik ini dalam hidupku,</i>

80
00:06:37,166 --> 00:06:40,375
<i>aku masih jauh dari menyerah</i>
<i>dan merepotkan mereka.</i>

81
00:06:40,458 --> 00:06:41,625
Berlindung!

82
00:06:45,375 --> 00:06:46,458
Tembak!

